Title: Analyzed Behavioral Data from Rat Memory Task Experiments
Creator: Deep Brain Lab, Sound and Multimedia Department, Politechnika Gdańsk
Subject: To analyze and interpret behavioral performance under various memory task protocols, including sequence retrieval and auditory feedback.
Description: This dataset contains analyzed behavioral data collected from experiments designed to track performance in memory tasks. The data includes session details, parsed sequences, event timestamps, and auditory stimuli.
